        public static MediaObjectList retrieveTagsForUser(UserIdentity authenticatedUser,
                                                  DataGroups dataGroups,
                                                  Limits limits,
                                                  SortOptions sortOptions)
        Parameters:
        authenticatedUser -
        dataGroups -
        limits - only the amount of results is processed for the limits. This is because the results are randomly generated, and thus have no order which could be used for paging.
        sortOptions - sort options are ignored. This is because of the complexity of the sort operations performed for randomly generated data.
        Returns:
        example list of media objects for the given values
